code: /**  * The strategy should always produce the QName that  * it was given on the constructor  */ @Test public void testQName() {     QName elementName = new QName("http://my.name.org", "myElement").     QNameStrategy strategy = new QNameStrategy(elementName).     QName actualElementName = strategy.findQNameForSoapActionOrType(null, GetCustomersByName.class).     Assert.assertEquals(elementName, actualElementName). }
